<h1>{{ title }}</h1>
<p>Welcome to {{ title }}</p>
<p>Use double braces to render text (escape html).</p>
<p>Here is a condition param: {{ condition }}</p>
<p>Use tripple braces to not escape html: {{{ param3 }}}</p>
<p>Helper functions.</p>
<p>Block (multiline) use # after braces and end with /</p>
<p>Evaluate conditions:</p>
{{# if condition }}
    Condition is met
    {{ else }}
    Condition is not met
{{/if}}

<p>Loop thru arrays!</p>
{{# each arrData}}
    {{ this }}
{{/each}}
<br>
{{# each arrData as |val key|}}
    key:{{ key }} value:{{ val }} <br>
{{/each}}


